    "To illustrate this, we apply two versions of the CMP algorithm to the electionsimulator data of Shirani and Bayati (2025), which replicates the voter mobilization experiment of Bond et al. (2012).",
    "The simulator generates a synthetic social network and records voting intentions for 20,000 users beginning 40 days before election day.",
